						<button class="addNewAddressBtn collapsed rounded-pill" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
							data-bs-target="#newAddressFormCollapse" aria-expanded="false"
							aria-controls="newAddressFormCollapse">
							+ Add New Address
						</button>
						<div class="collapse" id="newAddressFormCollapse">
							<form id="addNewAddressForm">
								<div class="row">
									<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-2">
										<label class="mb-1 fw-normal" asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.StreetName">Street
											Name</label>
										<input type="text" asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.StreetName"
											class="form-control" placeholder="Street Name" />
										<span class="text-danger"
											asp-validation-for="addNewAddressViewModel.StreetName"></span>
									</div>
									<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-2">
										<label class="mb-1 fw-normal" asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.HouseNumber">House
											Number</label>
										<input type="text" asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.HouseNumber"
											class="form-control" placeholder="House Number" />
										<span class="text-danger"
											asp-validation-for="addNewAddressViewModel.HouseNumber"></span>
									</div>
									<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-2">
										<label class="mb-1 fw-normal" asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.PostalCode">Postal
											Code</label>
										<input type="text" asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.PostalCode"
											class="form-control" disabled readonly placeholder="Postal Code" />
									</div>
									<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-2">
										<label class="mb-1 fw-normal" asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.City">City</label>
										<input type="text" asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.City" class="form-control"
											disabled readonly />
									</div>
									<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-2">
										<label class="mb-1 fw-normal" asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.PhoneNumber">Phone
											Number</label>
										<div class="input-group flex-nowrap">
											<span class="input-group-text" id="addon-wrapping">+91</span>
											<input type="tel" class="form-control"
												asp-for="addNewAddressViewModel.PhoneNumber" placeholder="Phone Number"
												aria-label="Phone Number" aria-describedby="addon-wrapping" />
										</div>
										<span class="text-danger"
											asp-validation-for="addNewAddressViewModel.PhoneNumber"></span>
									</div>
									<div class="col-12 mb-2">
										<button class="save rounded-pill">Save</button>
										<a href="#newAddressFormCollapse"
											class="text-decoration-none cancel rounded-pill" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
											aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="newAddressFormCollapse">
											Cancel
										</a>
									</div>
								</div>
							</form>
						</div>
					</div>
					<span class="text-danger d-block my-1" id="tab3Error"></span>
					<hr />
					<button class="yourDetailsBtn continueBtn rounded-pill">Continue</button>
				</div>
				<div class="tab-pane fade" id="paymentTab" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="paymentTabBtn">
					<label>Pay securely with Helperland payment gateway!</label>
					<div class="form-check">
						<input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="termsAndCond" />
						<label class="form-check-label" for="termsAndCond">
							I accepted terms and conditions, the cancellation policy and the privacy policy. I confirm
							that Helperland starts to
							execute the contract before the expiry of the withdrawal period and I lose my right of
							withdrawal as a consumer with full
							performance of the contract.
						</label>
					</div>
					<div class="bookServiceErr text-danger"></div>
					<button id="bookService" class="continueBtn rounded-pill">Complete Booking</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<button data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#paymentSummaryModal"
			class="summaryContainerToggleButton text-nowrap m-auto position-fixed bottom-0 start-50 w-auto translate-middle-x d-inline-block d-md-none text-white rounded-pill bg-success py-2 px-4 border-0 rounded-bottom">
			Payment Summary
		</button>

		<div class="summaryContainerRow col-12 col-md-5 col-lg-4 sticky-md-top">
			<div class="modal fade" id="paymentSummaryModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
				<div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
					<div class="summaryContainer modal-content rounded-0 border-0 mb-0 mb-md-3">
						<div class="summaryTitle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
							<span>Payment Summary</span>
							<button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white d-block d-md-none"
								data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
						</div>
						<div class="summaryContent bg-white">
							<div class="summaryHeader">Date And Time</div>
							<div class="serviceDateAndTimeSummary"><span id="serviceDateAndTimeSummaryDate"></span>
								<span id="serviceDateAndTimeSummaryTime"></span>
							</div>
							<div class="summaryHeader">Duration</div>
							<div class="serviceIndividualTime d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
								<span>Basic</span>
								<span id="ServiceBasicHoursText">6.5 Hrs.</span>
							</div>
							<div class="extraServiceContainer"></div>
							<hr />
							<div class="totalServiceTime d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
								<span class="fw-bold">Total Service Time</span>
								<span class="fw-bold">0 Hrs.</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<hr class="m-0" />
						<div class="totalPaymentContainer bg-white">
							<div class="totalPayment d-flex align-items-end justify-content-between">
								<span class="fw-normal">Total Payment</span>
								<div class="fw-bold">00.00 €</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="summaryFooter d-flex">
							<img asp-append-version="true" src="~/images/book-service-smiley.png" />
							<div class="summmaryFooterText" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#includedServices">
								See
								what
								is always included</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="paymentFaqs">
				<div class="paymentFaqsHeader text-center mt-3 mt-md-0">Questions?</div>
				<div class="faqContainer mb-3">
					<div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
						<div class="accordion-item border-0">
							<div class="accordion-header" id="faq0">
								<div class="accordion-btn collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
									data-bs-target="#collapse0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse0">
									<img asp-append-version="true" src="~/images/right-arrow-dark.png"
										alt="expandImage" />
									<span class="question align-middle">What's included in a
										cleaning?</span>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div id="collapse0" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq0"
								data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
								<div class="accordion-body">Bedroom, Living Room &amp; Common Areas,
									Bathrooms, Kitchen,
									Extras</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="accordion-item border-0">
							<div class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
								<div class="accordion-btn collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
									data-bs-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1">
									<img asp-append-version="true" src="~/images/right-arrow-dark.png"
										alt="expandImage" />
									<span class="question align-middle">Which Helperland professional
										will come to my
										place?</span>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq1"
								data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
								<div class="accordion-body">
									Helperland has a vast network of experienced, top-rated cleaners.
									Based on the time
									and date of your request, we
									work to assign the best professional available. Like working with a
									specific pro?
									Add them to your Pro Team from
									the mobile app and they'll be requested first for all future
									bookings. You will
									receive an email with details
									about your professional prior to your appointment.
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="accordion-item border-0">
							<div class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
								<div class="accordion-btn collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
									data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
									<img asp-append-version="true" src="~/images/right-arrow-dark.png"
										alt="expandImage" />
									<span class="question align-middle">Can I skip or reschedule
										bookings?</span>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2"
								data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
								<div class="accordion-body">
									You can reschedule any booking for free at least 24 hours in advance
									of the
									scheduled start time. If you need to
									skip a booking within the minimum commitment, we’ll credit the value
									of the booking
									to your account. You can use
									this credit on future cleanings and other Helperland services.
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<a class="faqLink" target="_blank" asp-controller="Static" asp-action="Faq">For More Help</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="loaderContainer">
	<div class="loader rounded-circle"></div>
</div>
</div>
